#

Belgian Waffles

25 min
$8
400 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

GlutenDairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Belgian

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

BreakfastBrunchSweet

Description

Light, fluffy, and golden brown waffles perfect for breakfast or brunch, topped with your favorite fruits or syrup.

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 2 cups
  • baking powder: 2 tablespoons
  • sugar: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1/2 teaspoon
  • eggs: 2 large
  • milk: 1 3/4 cups
  • unsalted butter: 1/2 cup, melted
  • vanilla extract: 1 teaspoon
